.contents
  - @users.each do |user|
    - if user.image.present?
      .user
        .user__image
          = link_to image_tag(user.image, class:"icon-image"),user_path(user.id)
        .user__name
          = user.name
    - else
      .user
        .user__image
          = link_to image_tag("名無し.png", class:"icon-image"),user_path(user.id)
        .user__name
          = user.name
